      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "三人のアイドルに案内されて、とある場所を訪れていた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "was guided by the three idols to a certain place",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1333333351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが私達が所属する星見プロダクションの事務所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the office of Hoshimi Prods‚ the company we belong to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333339492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "広くて明るくて、窓からの眺めも最高なんですよ！\nとっても居心地いいから、つい長居しちゃうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's spacious‚ bright‚ and the view from the window is amazing!\nIt's so comfortable that I end up staying for a long time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0333342671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みなさんは頻繁に事務所に来ているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you come to the office often?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333342671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい\n出来るだけ事務所には顔を出すようにしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes\nI try to show my face in the office as often as possible",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7666676004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ここに来ると大抵誰かがいるので\nつい話し込んでしまうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I come here‚ there's usually someone there‚\nso I end up talking to them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1666676004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。待ち合わせした訳じゃないのに\n気が付いたらみんな集まってたりするよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes. We don't have to make plans to see each other\nIt feels like everyone is here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2666658203,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6633333000023,
          "startTime": 42.5333291536
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ねーねー、ここにあったお菓子知らない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heyー Heyー‚ do you know where the cookies that was here went?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2999991536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣！　収録中ですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei! We're recording now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4333324869,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66666670000296,
          "startTime": 46.5999991536
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……こんな感じで\nここではみんなリラックスしてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ well… something like this\nEveryone here is relaxed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4666658203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見プロの事務所は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does the Hoshimi Prods. office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5333307068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みなさんにとってホームのような感覚なのでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "feel like home to you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1333324869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。私達が帰って来る場所、という意識は\nあるかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe so. It feel like that's a place\nwe can return to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333324869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ここには、沢山の思い出があって\n家族のような仲間達がいますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many memories and\nfriends who are like family here",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0333324869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "私達はみんな、星見プロが大好きなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We all really love Hoshimi Prods!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5999973734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
