    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "無数の星々が現れては消えゆく群雄割拠のアイドル業界",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Countless stars appear and disappear in the highly competitive idol industry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2666706522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そこに地方で生まれた小さな芸能事務所が風穴を開けた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A small local entertainment company has brought a breath of fresh air to the area",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8333390991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsideshed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsideshed-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.1500039856
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsideshed-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsideshed-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4000039856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今最も注目を集める芸能事務所、星見プロダクションと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With Hoshimi Prods‚ the most popular entertainment company today‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2000039856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男性アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "新世代を代表するアイドル達の栄光の軌跡を辿ろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "let's follow the glorious path of idols representing the new generation",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5660045187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_evening",
      "startTime": 108.0499963562
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 108.299964803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "番組が始まりましたわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The show has begun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0999963562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いろんな分野で活躍する人達を密着取材する\n人気のドキュメンタリー番組か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A popular documentary show that closely follows people\nactive in various fields…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666663289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "こんな有名な番組で私達を取り上げてもらえるなんて\nなんだか感慨深いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm deeply touched that such a famous show\nis covering us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9999996622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "しかもアイドルだけじゃなくて、事務所の星見プロまで\n特集してくれるなんてびっくりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's suprising that they not only idols\nbut also the Hoshimi Prods. office appeared",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4999996622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "人気グループが多数所属……その内の三組がBIG4\n星見プロが注目されるのは当然……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many popular groups are affiliated with it… three of them are BIG4\nOf course‚ Hoshimi Prods. is getting attention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6999996622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "密着取材するならこの私、成宮すずでしょうに\nテレビ局も見る目がありませんわね、まったく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to close coverage‚ it's me‚ Suzu Narumiya\nTV stations don't have any sense of it‚ really",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3999996622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は月スト、サニピ、トリエル、リズノワ、スリクス\nそれぞれのリーダーを密着取材する企画だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ Moon Tempest‚ Sunny Peace‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ LizNoir‚ and ⅢX\nIt's a plan to close coverage the leaders of each team",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5666663289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば{user}君も\nこの番組から取材を受けたのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ {user}-kun\nwas also interviewed on this show‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.7666663289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はい。「星見プロを支える若き敏腕マネージャー」\nなんて持ち上げられて……。勘弁してほしいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. 「A young and talented manager who supports Hoshimi Prods.」\nI'm really flattered…. I wish they would do it gently",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6333329956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
