    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ですが、その時のライブバトルは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ that live battle at that time is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.2999612609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大会屈指の名勝負として今も語り継がれています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "still mentioned as one of the best matches in the tournament",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 349.9666297078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その後始まったアイドルの祭典、I-UNITYでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ TRINITYAiLE was also noticed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.8666279275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルは優勝候補として注目されていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "as a candidate to win at the I-UNITY idol festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.7666297078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "当時BIG4だったⅢXとの対戦、そして待ち焦がれた\nサニピとの再戦を私達も楽しみにしていたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were looking forward to match against IIIX‚ who were part of BIG4 at the time‚\nand the long-awaited revenge match against Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.9332963745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 370.4332945942
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "それが叶うことはありませんでした\n結局、I-UNITYはサニーピースが優勝して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That never happened\nIn the end‚ Sunny Peace won I-UNITY…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 373.5999630411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "事務所を辞めて行き場を失った私達は、サニピが\n所属する星見プロに二度も拾ってもらったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After we left the office and lost our place to go‚\nHoshimi Prods‚ which Sunny Peace is a part of‚ took us in twice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 381.0332963745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トリエルと同時期にリズノワが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the same time as TRINITYAiLE‚ LizNoir‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 384.7999612609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "少し遅れてスリクスも星見プロへ移籍しましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and a little later‚ ⅢX also moved to Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 387.4666297078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロは行き場を失った私達の\n受け皿になってくれました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hoshimi Prods. became a place for us\nwho had lost our way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 394.5332963745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 396.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
