      "text": "あの時、みんなが手を差し伸べてくれたから\n今の私達があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are who we are today because\neveryone reached out to us at that time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.2332963745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロには感謝しています。だからこそ\nこのご恩は返さなければいけないと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I am grateful to Hoshimi Prods. That is why\nI feel I need to repay this favor",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 406.2332800984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になって、名実ともにアイドルの頂点に立つ\n――それが、私達から星見プロへの恩返しです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Becoming part of BIG4 and standing at the top of idol ranks\n――That is our way of giving back to Hoshimi Prods.",
